    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LA-series — washers</h3><p>Fagor's commercial washer line across capacity tiers: LA-14 (14kg/30lb), LA-25 (55lb), LA-35 (77lb), LA-60 (130lb), LA-90 (200lb), LA-110 (240lb), LA-180 (400lb). Hotel central laundry + hospital OPL + restaurant linen applications. Service: pressure switch, water-inlet valves (multiple on larger capacity), door lock + interlock, bearing assembly, inverter drive, chemistry-pump integration.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LR-series — tumble dryers</h3><p>Tumble dryers matched to LA washer capacities. Gas or electric heated. Service: burner + ignitor + flame sensor + gas valve (gas variants); heating element (electric); door switch, drum rollers, belt, air-flow pressure switch, exhaust thermistor.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LN-series — flatwork ironer</h3><p>Large rotary drum ironer for sheet + tablecloth + hospital linen processing. Hotel central laundry + hospital + restaurant-linen operations that process flat fabric at scale. Service: heated drum surface, padding replacement, guide rollers, steam-system integration (steam-heated variants), temperature control.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>LD-series — dry-cleaning</h3><p>Dry-cleaning machines. Less common in LA commercial laundry installations but present at specialty dry-cleaners and some hotel + hospital operations with integrated dry-cleaning capability. Service: perchloroethylene or hydrocarbon solvent recovery systems, filtration, distillation components.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Chemistry + controls integration</h3><p>Fagor Industrial washers integrate with chemistry-dispensing systems (Ecolab, Hydro Systems, comparable). PLC controls on larger-capacity units. European electrical conventions adapted to North American voltage — our techs carry metric + standard tooling.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Sibling to Fagor commercial dishwashers</h3><p>Fagor Industrial's commercial dishwasher line (AD series undercounter, CO conveyor, FI flight-type) is the same brand under the same Onnera Group parent. Mixed kitchen + laundry Fagor installs route through single Onnera Group parts channel.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

